      "isEnabled": true,
      "name": "SeaDex",
      "pattern": "(?i)\\b(?:seadex|best[\\s.-]?release|alt[\\s.-]?(?:best[\\s.-]?)?release)\\b|ᴀʟᴛ ʀᴇʟᴇᴀsᴇ|ʙᴇsᴛ ʀᴇʟᴇᴀsᴇ",
